Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來進行契約的儀式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美…美智留？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿倫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那啥…我們…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為我會這麼簡單就原諒你剛才對我做的事嗎 阿倫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:34.85,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 冰堂同學成為了我們的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好期待呢 她寫出來的歌真的好棒
