Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:09.02,bgmj1,NTP,0,0,0,,君は聴こえる?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:11.81,bgmj1,NTP,0,0,0,,僕のこの声が
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:14.49,bgmj1,NTP,0,0,0,,闇に虚しく
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:17.02,bgmj1,NTP,0,0,0,,吸い込まれた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,bgmj1,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:20.03,bgmj1,NTP,0,0,0,,もしも世界が
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:22.79,bgmj1,NTP,0,0,0,,意味を持つのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:25.55,bgmj1,NTP,0,0,0,,こんな気持ちを
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:27.65,bgmj1,NTP,0,0,0,,無駄ではない?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,bgmj1,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:31.08,bgmj1,NTP,0,0,0,,憧れに押しつぶされて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.14,0:10:33.81,bgmj1,NTP,0,0,0,,あきらめてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:36.51,bgmj1,NTP,0,0,0,,果てしない空の色も
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:39.06,bgmj1,NTP,0,0,0,,知らないで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,bgmj1,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:44.24,bgmj1,NTP,0,0,0,,走り出した想いが今でも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:50.04,bgmj1,NTP,0,0,0,,この胸を確かに叩いてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:55.32,bgmj1,NTP,0,0,0,,今日の僕がその先に続く
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:11:01.18,bgmj1,NTP,0,0,0,,僕らなりの明日を築いていく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,bgmj1,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:10.13,bgmj1,NTP,0,0,0,,答えはそう　いつもここにある
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:09.02,bgmc1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能聽得見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:11.81,bgmc1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:14.49,bgmc1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是說終會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:17.02,bgmc1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}消逝在那黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:17.02,bgmc1,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:20.03,bgmc1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果說世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:22.79,bgmc1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}擁有它自己的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:25.55,bgmc1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我的這份感情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:27.65,bgmc1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也不是白費的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:27.65,bgmc1,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:31.08,bgmc1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被人們的憧憬壓垮了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.14,0:10:33.81,bgmc1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想暗自放棄之時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:36.51,bgmc1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可我連那無邊無際的天空的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:39.06,bgmc1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:39.06,bgmc1,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:44.24,bgmc1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奔跑的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:50.04,bgmc1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如今也在敲擊著我的心門
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:55.32,bgmc1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天的我將會連接未來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:11:01.18,bgmc1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}構築我們的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:11:01.18,bgmc1,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:10.13,bgmc1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}答案 一直在我們的心中
